    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, and is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and it still carries that 'new car' scent. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the premium infotainment system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is perfect. It has been strictly garage-kept and has never seen rain or snow. All scheduled maintenance has been performed exclusively at the dealership, with a complete binder of service records included. The engine bay is immaculate, and the tires are brand-new performance-grade rubber. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
